reviewText: Dvd arrived promptly.  A little bit of wear regarding the cover.  Dvd functioned well.  Reasonably priced.
Came very quickly and my little girl is so happy there is more to her addition. It plays well and case looks almost new.

My son loves Max and Ruby and this dvd was no exception.  His only complained was that it was not long enough.
It is a little shorter than many of the others.
